This is a simple To-Do list web application developed using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, and Session Storage (no database). It allows users to add, delete, and clear tasks during their active session.

🚀 Features
Add tasks to a to-do list

Delete individual tasks

Clear all tasks at once

Session-based storage (tasks will reset when session ends)

⚙️ Tech Stack
Java 17

Spring Boot 3.4.4

Spring MVC

Thymeleaf (for frontend)

Maven

WAR Packaging (deployable on external Tomcat)

