🛠️ How to Run
1. Clone the Repository
bash
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/kannan-ramesh/todospringboot.git
cd todospringboot/todo1
2. Build the WAR
bash
Copy
Edit
mvn clean package
3. Deploy on Tomcat
Copy the generated target/todo1.war file to your Apache Tomcat webapps/ folder.

Start Tomcat and visit:

bash
Copy
Edit
http://localhost:8080/todo1/todo
📋 Sample Usage
🟢 Add Task: Type in the input box and click "add".

🗑️ Delete Task: Click the "delete" button next to a task.

❌ Delete All: Click "Delete All" to remove every task from the list.

📌 Notes
Tasks are stored in the HTTP session, not in a database.

Session ends = tasks disappear.
